What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Rugged Industrial Display Market?
Market Analysis and Size
The growth of the market is impelled by the developing technological shift in display technology and the development of rugged display devices with high specifications, decreased total cost of ownership (TCO) offered by ruggedized products compared to consumer-grade devices in harsh environments, and increasing demand for HMI and IoT in various industries. Growing demand for human-machine interferences (HMI) and the Internet of Things (IoT) in numerous end-use industries is foreseen to boost the usage of rugged displays. The growth among segments helps you analyze niche pockets of growth and strategies to approach the market and determine your core application areas and the differences in your target markets.
